message:
Add seed_system_decks() to populate 3 decks with 16 voices

- Deck 1: Introspection (6 voices from existing config.py)
- Deck 2: Scholar (6 academic voices with placeholder prompts)
- Deck 3: Philosophy (4 philosophical voices with placeholder prompts)
- Idempotent seeding (safe to run multiple times)
- Called automatically from init_db()
